To install, be sure to define the Boost and HDF5 locations by
./configure --with-boost=/path/to/boost --with-hdf5=/path/to/hdf5


Tests written in python which generate data for running wham using
a known potential function, then compare the wham results to the
analytic function are located in tests/schemes/{quad,flat,nobias}/.
Be sure to change the call to python to your local python binary.
Requires:
    matplotlib
    numpy
    scipy
